{
  "text": "In a similar way, we obtain a coalgebraic duality for L-ML-algebras (i.e., algebras of a version of Fitting's many-valued modal logic). We remark that [30, Lemma 2.6] is useful when proving that n is semi-primal (this can be shown in a similar way to [CITATION_1] Lemma 2.3] via [CITATION_2] Lemma 2.6] ).",
